Several techniques are available82, 85 to estimate the individual γi. They generally require to perform specific analyses to extract the contribution of a particular feedback. One example is to perform an experiment when only the investigated feedback is operating and comparing the changes ΔTsi in this experiment to the one of the reference system ΔT0.13\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
