				\begin{document}$$\gamma _i = \frac{{{\mathrm{\Delta }}T_{{\mathrm{s}}i} - {\mathrm{\Delta }}T_{\mathrm{0}}}}{{{\mathrm{\Delta }}T_{{\mathrm{s}}i}}}.$$\end{document}γi=ΔTsi-ΔT0ΔTsi.This solution is not the one traditionally used for radiative feedbacks but the approach can be generalized to any feedback where this alternative may be a practical solution for feedback evaluation.
